org.jasig.cas.authentication
类 ImmutableAuthentication

java.lang.Object
  org.jasig.cas.authentication.ImmutableAuthentication
所有已实现的接口：
Serializable, Authentication
public final class ImmutableAuthentication
extends Object
implements Authentication, Serializable

Immutable authentication event whose attributes may not change after creation. This class is designed for serialization and is suitable for long-term storage.

从以下版本开始：
3.0
作者：
Dmitriy Kopylenko, Scott Battaglia, Marvin S. Addison

ImmutableAuthentication

public ImmutableAuthentication(Date date,
                               List<CredentialMetaData> credentials,
                               Principal principal,
                               Map<String,Object> attributes,
                               Map<String,HandlerResult> successes,
                               Map<String,Class<? extends Exception>> failures)
Creates a new instance with the given data.

参数：
date - Non-null authentication date.
credentials - Non-null list of credential metadata containing at least one entry.
principal - Non-null authenticated principal.
attributes - Nullable map of authentication metadata.
successes - Non-null map of authentication successes containing at least one entry.
failures - Nullable map of authentication failures.

getCredentials

public List<CredentialMetaData> getCredentials()
从接口 Authentication 复制的描述
Gets a list of metadata about the credentials supplied at authentication time.

指定者：
接口 Authentication 中的 getCredentials
返回：
Non-null list of supplied credentials represented as metadata that should be considered safe for long-term storage (e.g. serializable and secure with respect to credential disclosure). The order of items in the returned list SHOULD be the same as the order in which the source credentials were presented and subsequently processed.

getFailures

public Map<String,Class<? extends Exception>> getFailures()
从接口 Authentication 复制的描述
Gets a map describing failed authentications. By definition the failures here were not sufficient to prevent authentication.

指定者：
接口 Authentication 中的 getFailures
返回：
Map of authentication handler names to the authentication errors produced on attempted authentication.
